Generic single-database configuration with async support for asyncpg.

This configuration is set up to work with asyncpg and PostgreSQL.

To run migrations:

    alembic upgrade head

To create a new migration:

    alembic revision -m "description"

To rollback:

    alembic downgrade -1

For more information, see the Alembic documentation:
https://alembic.sqlalchemy.org/

